[{"ave_id":"AVE-2005-0002","file_name":"2005/AVE-2005-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2005-0851","title":"FileZilla Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FileZilla Server 存在远程拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 FTP 服务端口（默认 21）发送特制的 MKD 命令（包含超长字符串或空字节），触发服务进程空指针解引用异常，导致 FileZilla Server 服务崩溃终止，影响正常的 FTP 文件传输服务可用性。该漏洞影响 FileZilla Server 0.9.8d 及之前版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2005-0851"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2005-05-02","updated":"2005-05-02","remediation":"升级 FileZilla Server 至 0.9.6 或更高版本。如无法立即升级，可在服务器配置中禁用 MODE Z（zlib 压缩）功能，以阻止攻击者通过触发 zlib 解压死循环耗尽服务器资源。建议定期关注 FileZilla 官方更新通知，及时应用安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2005/CVE-2005-0851.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2005/CVE-2005-0851.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/network/cves/2005/CVE-2005-0851.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2005/0xxx/CVE-2005-0851.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2005/CVE-2005-0851","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/23b9072d94002e85c65869c9b10a30b4a0f4057c/CVE/data/2005/CVE-2005-0851.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2005/CVE-2005-0851.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2005-0851_8.yaml","https://github.com/roy9495/CVE-Extractor/blob/21bc96060eb3124bb762be8e16b95c7e2b15d4dc/cvelistV5-main/cves/2005/0xxx/CVE-2005-0851.json","https://github.com/michael1981/sfish_pt/blob/14f609d56e35e9810a1de14712293ab47cc03a46/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%2B%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%2B%E7%88%86%E7%A0%B4/X-Scan-v3.3/plugins/filezilla_denial.nasl","https://github.com/method-security/networkscan/blob/3d96ce1c284d56cc401537336d2d45421a1c27fd/utils/nuclei/templates/cve/2005/CVE-2005-0851.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2005/AVE-2005-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2005-0007","file_name":"2005/AVE-2005-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2005-4385","title":"Cofax Cofax 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Cofax 2.0 RC3 及之前版本的 search.htm 页面存在跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 searchstring 参数注入恶意 Web 脚本或 HTML 代码实施攻击。当管理员或用户访问被利用的链接时，恶意脚本将在受害者浏览器中执行，可能导致会话劫持、敏感信息泄露等危害。该漏洞影响 Cofax 1.9.9c/1.9.9d/2.0 RC1/2.0 RC2/2.0 RC3 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2005-4385"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2005-12-20T02:03:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:18:42.187","remediation":"对 search.htm 中 searchstring 参数进行严格的输入过滤与输出编码，过滤 <script>、onerror 等危险关键字并 HTML 实体编码输出。由于 Cofax 项目已停止维护无官方补丁，建议迁移至活跃维护的 CMS 系统，或在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）层面添加规则拦截包含 XSS 特征的请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://pridels0.blogspot.com/2005/12/cofax-xss-vuln.html","http://www.osvdb.org/21850","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/15940","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2005/2977","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/26879","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-4385.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2005/CVE-2005-4385.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-4385.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2005-4385.js","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2005-4385_1.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2005-4385-1321.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2005-4385_35.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2005-4385-1320.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/cve-2005-4385-1322.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8aea42c71147e21c6d32b71ffce877107de995c6/cves/2005/4xxx/CVE-2005-4385.json","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2005-4385-1321.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2005/AVE-2005-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2005-0006","file_name":"2005/AVE-2005-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2005-3634","title":"SAP Web Application Server URI 重定向漏洞","description":"SAP Web Application Server 6.10 至 7.00 版本的 BSP 运行环境中的 frameset.htm 存在 URI 重定向漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 sap-sessioncmd 参数传递 close 命令、同时在 sap-exiturl 参数中构造恶意 URL，诱使已登录用户退出系统并重定向至任意外部网站，从而实施钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响 SAP Web Application Server 6.x 及 7.0 系列版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布安全补丁，建议用户升级至修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2005-3634"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2005-11-16T21:22:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:17:18.450","remediation":"建议升级 SAP Web Application Server 至 7.00 之后的补丁版本，安装对应 SAP Security Note 修复包。如无法升级，可在 SAP Web Dispatcher 或反向代理层配置 URL 过滤规则，拦截包含 sap-sessioncmd=close 及 sap-exiturl 参数的外部请求，同时加强对 exiturl 参数的白名单校验以防止未授权重定向。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=113156525006667&w=2","http://secunia.com/advisories/17515/","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/163","http://www.cybsec.com/vuln/CYBSEC_Security_Advisory_Multiple_XSS_in_SAP_WAS.pdf","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/15362","http://www.securitytracker.com/alerts/2005/Nov/1015174.html","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2005/2361","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/23031","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/26488","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3634.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2005/CVE-2005-3634.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3634.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8aea42c71147e21c6d32b71ffce877107de995c6/cves/2005/3xxx/CVE-2005-3634.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2005-3634_4.yaml","https://github.com/youki992/VscanPlus/blob/714a0e276a538a22c1a6215c71458a8b59a920ef/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3634.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2005-3634_4.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2005-3634_7.yaml","https://github.com/elijah-bennett0/IntentLimit/blob/bcfe225cf61ee454aa53896f7f3120246f52119f/tools/exploitation/GoldenBullet/exploits/cve_2005_3634/cve_2005_3634.py","https://github.com/rjp2525/cve-data/blob/2f3ce5ef3a11f37d0a2e7d88f12b74499612a438/2005/CVE-2005-3634.json","https://github.com/daffainfo/cvelist/blob/37b3071167a2a3fb5757922e970775326b735d8f/cves/2005/3xxx/CVE-2005-3634.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2005/AVE-2005-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2005-0005","file_name":"2005/AVE-2005-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2005-3344","title":"Debian Horde 默认管理员空密码漏洞","description":"Horde 3.0.4 默认安装中存在一个未设置密码的管理员账户，远程攻击者无需任何认证即可通过该空密码账户直接登录 Horde 应用管理后台，获取完全控制权限。该漏洞影响 Debian 系统上预装的 Horde 3.0.4 版本，由于安装脚本在初始化时未强制要求设置管理员密码，导致攻击者可通过默认凭据直接进入系统，进而可能访问或篡改邮件数据、联系人信息及其他敏感资料。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2005-3344"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2005-11-16T07:42:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:16:46.050","remediation":"建议立即升级 Horde 至修复版本：Debian Sarge 用户升级至 horde3 3.0.4-4sarge1，Sid 用户升级至 3.0.5-2，运行 apt-get update && apt-get upgrade horde3。升级后第一时间登录后台为 admin 账户设置强密码，如不使用默认管理员账户则应直接禁用或删除该账户。手动安装用户可从 debian.org/security/2005/dsa-884 下载补丁包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/2005/dsa-884","http://www.networkscanning.com/Horde-Default-Admin-Password-Vulnerability-VSS_20171.html","http://www.osvdb.org/24117","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/15337/","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/24576","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3344.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2005/CVE-2005-3344.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3344.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2005-3344.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2005-3344-1316.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2005-3344_1.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/1ef87e5a137977cc6b834fe9cd2a28af09211ff8/2005/CVE-2005-3344.json","https://github.com/michael1981/sfish_pt/blob/14f609d56e35e9810a1de14712293ab47cc03a46/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%2B%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%2B%E7%88%86%E7%A0%B4/X-Scan-v3.3/plugins/horde_default_passwd.nasl","https://github.com/runZeroInc/nuclei-templates/blob/89af8e391d368228625addfe3ecc6aee3b5d0345/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3344.yaml","https://github.com/RogoLabs/vuln-anarchy/blob/0c6200c95a1271966d9eba8cd917eb07d27921e7/docs/data/2005/CVE-2005-3344.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--053837d0-cebb-4cd7-bcb2-f6db6847ebc1.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2005/AVE-2005-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2005-0004","file_name":"2005/AVE-2005-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2005-3128","title":"SquirrelMail Address Add Plugin 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"SquirrelMail 的 Address Add 插件 1.9 及 2.0 版本中的 add.php 存在跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 IMG 标签注入恶意 Web 脚本或 HTML 代码实施攻击。当管理员或用户访问被注入恶意代码的页面时，脚本将在浏览器中执行，可能导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 SquirrelMail 1.4.2 及安装了受影响插件的环境，攻击无需认证，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2005-3128"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2005-10-04T22:02:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:16:18.220","remediation":"升级 SquirrelMail 至 1.4.3a 或更高版本，该版本已修复 add.php 的 XSS 问题。如无法升级，可删除 plugins/address_add/add.php 文件或卸载 Address Add 插件。同时配置 Web 应用防火墙对输入参数中 IMG 标签进行过滤作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=306172","http://lists.apple.com/archives/security-announce//2007/Jul/msg00004.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=112801672520766&w=2","http://moritz-naumann.com/adv/0002/sqmadd/0002.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/16987/","http://secunia.com/advisories/26235","http://securitytracker.com/id?1014988","http://squirrelmail.org/plugin_view.php?id=101","http://www.mandriva.com/security/advisories?name=MDKSA-2005:178","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/14973","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/25159","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2007/2732","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/22453","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/26305","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3128.yaml","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-3128.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8aea42c71147e21c6d32b71ffce877107de995c6/cves/2005/3xxx/CVE-2005-3128.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2005/CVE-2005-3128","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2005/CVE-2005-3128.rules","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e64e866f5c799abe7f39eba36818200f3831f1cb/CVE/data/2005/CVE-2005-3128.json","https://github.com/onewinner/Lightx/blob/66baef13ea408675c6c144ae6e01b1df0a9278eb/config/pocs/CVE-2005-3128.yaml","https://github.com/elijah-bennett0/IntentLimit/blob/bcfe225cf61ee454aa53896f7f3120246f52119f/tools/exploitation/CrazyIngrate/exploits/cve_2005_3128/cve_2005_3128.py","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/1ef87e5a137977cc6b834fe9cd2a28af09211ff8/2005/CVE-2005-3128.json","https://github.com/michael1981/sfish_pt/blob/14f609d56e35e9810a1de14712293ab47cc03a46/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%2B%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%2B%E7%88%86%E7%A0%B4/X-Scan-v3.3/plugins/macosx_SecUpd2007-007.nasl","https://github.com/RogoLabs/consensus-engine/blob/c8cb8d393cb233bc0222f12dee382f3879140c3d/docs/data/2005/CVE-2005-3128.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2005/AVE-2005-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2005-0003","file_name":"2005/AVE-2005-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2005-2428","title":"IBM Lotus Domino names.nsf 敏感信息泄漏漏洞","description":"IBM Lotus Domino R5 和 R6 版本 WebMail 模块在启用\"为所有字段生成 HTML\"选项时，将 names.nsf 中的敏感数据存储在隐藏表单字段中。远程攻击者可通过查看 HTML 源码获取包括 HTTPPassword 字段中的密码哈希值、密码修改日期、客户端平台与机器名等敏感信息，导致凭据泄露。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2005-2428"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2005-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T22:14:52.093","remediation":"在 Domino Designer 中打开 Person 表单，在表单属性第 2 个标签页中取消勾选「Generate HTML for all fields（为所有字段生成 HTML）」；同时打开 $PersonalInheritableSchema 子表单，将 $dspHTTPPassword 和 HTTPPassword 字段的属性中「Hide paragraph from（隐藏段落对象）」勾选 Web 浏览器。建议同步升级至 IBM Lotus Domino R7 及以上版本以彻底修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=112240869130356&w=2","http://secunia.com/advisories/16231/","http://securitytracker.com/id?1014584","http://www-1.ibm.com/support/docview.wss?uid=swg21212934","http://www.cybsec.com/vuln/default_configuration_information_disclosure_lotus_domino.pdf","http://www.osvdb.org/18462","http://www.securiteam.com/securitynews/5FP0E15GLQ.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/14389","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/21556","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/39495/","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/39495","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-2428.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2005/CVE-2005-2428.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/a8dd65f3bd9f09f4c40ddbec294c8d30c1b24bd7/2005/CVE-2005-2428.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/69a5a3cf926251a00061ec14d208b227367df73d/http/cves/2005/CVE-2005-2428.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/cve-2005-2428-1310.yaml","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2005/CVE-2005-2428/poc/others/README.md","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder3/cve-2005-2428-1309.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/TPALL/ARPSyndicate/nuclei/cvescan/medium/CVE-2005-2428.yaml","ht